{"tid":1972210,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林鄭月娥：盡最大努力阻止失業浪潮出現","createTime":"2020-04-14T11:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T11:32:05.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8a4acbe7fcc1ee69b3fe0da88744f853e9df1d89","tid":1972210,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:29:04.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，關心失業問題，盡最大努力阻止失業浪潮出現，政府推出的保就業計劃，目的是要阻截更多失業情況出現。<br />\n<br />\n她指，僱主只能選擇以1月至3月其中一個月計算補助，相信較多僱主會選擇疫情爆發前的1月，因為當時為應對農曆新年僱員人數應該最多，如果僱主的業務有起色，可以請回人手，但僱主如果無辦法，僱員亦可透過放寬綜援資產限額上限一倍等措施得到紓緩。"},{"pid":"c0fc88c9420d54b17d74d9c302e77d7badd26a0b","tid":1972210,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:29:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1280732&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWcWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=b327163c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280732</a>"},{"pid":"60e8b5c74755d1355149b0ba974b786cc14bd51f","tid":1972210,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:32:05.000Z","msg":"政府應該宣布全面取消限制人群措施<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1972035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1972035</a>"}]}